reviewText:
An awesome collection of music videos...most of them you can't get anywhere else! The whole music video list is as follows:

1)The Black Crows - High Head Blues

2)Dave Matthews Band - What Would You Say

3)All-4-One - Skillz

4)Martin Page - In The House Of Stone & Light

5)Donna Summer - Melody Of Love

6)Christopher Williams - Dance 4 Me

7)Adam Ant - Wonderful

8)Joshua Kadison - Beau's All Night Radio Love Line

9)Messiah - I Fell Love

10)London Jones - Save Our Love

11)The Beatles - Can't Buy Me Love
